{"tid":2130760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記住呢間黃店","createTime":"2020-07-29T11:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T17:01:11.000Z","uid":34409,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9460fdd3d1410442b09e03626c5b490af2969819","tid":2130760,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T11:43:51.000Z","msg":"將來再開後一定食爆佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1869150173331019/posts/2722589951320366/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1869150173331019%2Fposts%2F2722589951320366%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6SaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=4b55a7ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1869150173331019/posts/2722589951320366/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n~內部裝修~特別停業通知~<br />\n<br />\n冷氣如常開放<br />\n<br />\n未來1星期，內部裝修停業期間，由中午12點至3點，香港人可自由內進兼且免費自行提取防疫用品。<br />\n<br />\n無員工丶無廁所、無食物、無飲品提供。內進前請自行量度體溫消毒雙手，每枱只限二人。<br />\n<br />\n敬請自行處理垃圾，清潔枱面，使用後盡快離開，方便其他人使用。<br />\n<br />\n天氣無情，人間有愛，助己助人。<br />\n<br />\n#香港人加油<br />\n#香港人高汁<br />\n#自己香港自己救<br />\n#外賣訂茶咖里"},{"pid":"eb5cdafc9402e8c05c9d938fd5cf85ac75f7a2cf","tid":2130760,"uid":235727,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T11:50:21.000Z","msg":"茶咖里 茶咖宅<br />\n<br />\n兩間都耐唔耐會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a44f6d56b03f55dc23cedf55da3eb2c6be32cc9d","tid":2130760,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T11:51:05.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"89389db8fe106b42ff2204bcace3ae143db4cca2","tid":2130760,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T11:51:54.000Z","msg":"<strong></strong>"},{"pid":"134743d23412ba1c3dd8f826849b9ddf6da46a57","tid":2130760,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T11:52:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1c8927b920667f88800ec6c8296544738b0af9f","tid":2130760,"uid":6840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020